jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/d/5/4/thumb_277116180.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/2/b/e/thumb_268988894.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/1/8/c/thumb_277944972.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/6/3/6/thumb_283766166.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/7/0/4/thumb_283430948.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/d/1/7/thumb_267892503.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/d/8/0/3/thumb_262975299.jpeg\" /></div>          </div>          <p style=\"line-height:16px\">* WordPress Helpdesk * If you have a WordPress site and you&#8217;ve got a bug or there is something you are not quite sure how to do, come and meet the WordPress professionals who may be able to help you or point you in the right direction. Given that WordPress 5.0 is likely to have been released before the end of 2018, there will be a special focus on &#8230;</p>     </div>     <p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Glasgow-WordPress-Meetup/events/255764169/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"mu_button\"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>&#8220;Yoast&#8221; by Kayleigh Thorpe and &#8220;Digital Marketing&#8221; by Valerie Ferrat</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuesday 26th <strong>February</strong> 2019, from 6:00pm until 8:30pm at the <a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/6PEABmAejeB2\">Old Sheriff Court (Scottish Youth Theatre venue)</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Two talks. We&#8217;ll be updating the event description as soon as we have all the details!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-meetup-com wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-meetup\"><